          <text><![CDATA[<p>Honors the 100th Anniversary of the World War I Christmas Truce of 1914, and recognizes the Truce's symbol of the triumph of the human spirit over adversity.</p> <p> Commemorates the Christmas Truce of 1914 and its legacy as a message of future peace and unity between all nations.</p>]]></text>
